## Ingredients

- [ ] tomato, sliced
- [ ] mozzarella ball, sliced
- [ ] extra virgin olive oil, the good stuff
- [ ] basil
- [ ] oregano
- [ ] ground pepper
- [ ] baguette

## Recipe

1. Slice the tomatoes and mozzarella. Drizzle olive oil on top with a small amount of balsamic vinegar
1. For the bread, add a bowl of ground pepper and olive oil for dipping
